snippet: Two men have been charged with raping a 16-year-old girl at a Johns Hopkins University fraternity party.
abstract: Chaz Haggins and Ethan Turner of Reisterstown, Md, are charged with raping 16-year-old girl at Johns Hopkins University fraternity party; men are not university students but fraternity is suspended.
lead_paragraph: Two men have been charged with raping a 16-year-old girl at a Johns Hopkins University fraternity party.

headline.main: Maryland: Two Are Charged With Rape at Fraternity House
